Package: sampcompR
Title: Comparing and Visualizing Differences Between Surveys
Version: 0.2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bjoern", "Rohr",  email= "Bjoern.Rohr@gesis.org", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = 0000-0001-6504-9516))
Description: A bundle of functions, to easily analyze and visualise differences 
    between samples or subsamples on three levels. The comparisons can be univariate,
    bivariate or multivariate. 
